ter 30</a>, Jaime IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Jaime VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403152759\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.070 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.253 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 840/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10640/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7168/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 701/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3288/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.48 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  243.171      1 -total\n 94.25%  229.188      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 93.49%  227.338      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.47%   30.316     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.91%   16.812      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.42%   10.752      7 Template:Ref\n  2.54%    6.165      7 Template:Ref/core\n  1.10%    2.667      1 Template:References\n  0.36%    0.870      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4122-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403152759 and revision id 311501\n -->\n",
